  "title": "Site Coordinator",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description </strong></p><p>Corrosion Proof Construction (Asia) Pte Ltd is seeking a Site Coordinator to support daily site operations and coordination activities. The role involves assisting site teams, coordinating work activities, and ensuring smooth communication between site personnel and management. Training and guidance will be provided for suitable candidates.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities </strong></p><ul><li>Assist in coordinating daily site activities and operations</li><li>Support Site Supervisor / Project Team on site matters</li><li>Liaise with sub-contractors, suppliers, and internal teams</li><li>Assist in monitoring work progress and site schedules</li><li>Maintain basic site documentation and records</li><li>Report site issues or delays to the relevant supervisor</li><li>Perform other duties as assigned by management</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements </strong></p><ul><li><strong>Fresh graduates are welcome to apply</strong></li><li><strong>Candidates with own transport will have an advantage</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Minimum Qualification </strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or equivalent</li></ul><p><strong>Working Location </strong></p><ul><li>Project sites across Singapore</li></ul><p><strong>WorkingHours (Mandatory Field)</strong></p><ul><li>As per project / site requirements</li></ul><p><strong>Please fill up the e-application form if you are interested.</strong></p><ul><li><a href=\"https://forms.office.com/r/rJ08D21v5s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Application Form – Fill in form</a></li></ul>",
